  "title": "경복궁 야간개장 입장권 예매",
  "addDate": "2013. 5. 23.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110168660441",
  "html_size": 185168,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110168660441\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110168660441\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&#65279;어제. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">경복궁 야간개장 소식을 인터넷 포털에서 제목만 봤다.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">퇴근했더니</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">6살된 아들녀석이 '경복궁이 밤에도 한데요. 우리 가봐요'란다.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">아마도 뉴스에서 봤나보다.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">뭐... 어쩌겠는가. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">가야지.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;</span></p><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369285593031\"></span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369285593031\">&#65279;<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130523_205/isuhani_1369285584822YvRUe_JPEG/%B0%E6%BA%B9%B1%C3_%BE%DF%B0%A3%B0%B3%C0%E5_3.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"463\" height=\"306\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 463px; rheight: 306px\" id=\"20130523_205/isuhani_1369285584822YvRUe_JPEG/%B0%E6%BA%B9%B1%C3_%BE%DF%B0%A3%B0%B3%C0%E5_3.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A69059D9')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130523_205/isuhani_1369285584822YvRUe_JPEG/%B0%E6%BA%B9%B1%C3_%BE%DF%B0%A3%B0%B3%C0%E5_3.jpg?type=w3\"><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369285687188\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369285687188\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369285687356\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369285687356\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369285687500\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369285687500\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369285687044\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369285687044\">&#65279;</span></span></span> \r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">점심시간에 경복궁 야간개장 예매시스템에 접속한다.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">18세 미만 소아는 무료. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">그럼 성인 2명만 예매하면 되겠다.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130523_179/isuhani_1369285584662LDop8_JPEG/%B0%E6%BA%B9%B1%C3_%BE%DF%B0%A3%B0%B3%C0%E5_2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"332\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 448px\" id=\"20130523_179/isuhani_1369285584662LDop8_JPEG/%B0%E6%BA%B9%B1%C3_%BE%DF%B0%A3%B0%B3%C0%E5_2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A69059D9')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130523_179/isuhani_1369285584662LDop8_JPEG/%B0%E6%BA%B9%B1%C3_%BE%DF%B0%A3%B0%B3%C0%E5_2.jpg?type=w3\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">예매시스템은 요런 화면으로 시작한다.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">이름입력하고.. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">다음, 다음, 다음.. 결재.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">끝.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130523_8/isuhani_1369285584471Kz2dG_JPEG/%B0%E6%BA%B9%B1%C3_%BE%DF%B0%A3%B0%B3%C0%E5.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"224\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 740px; rheight: 302px\" id=\"20130523_8/isuhani_1369285584471Kz2dG_JPEG/%B0%E6%BA%B9%B1%C3_%BE%DF%B0%A3%B0%B3%C0%E5.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A69059D9')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130523_8/isuhani_1369285584471Kz2dG_JPEG/%B0%E6%BA%B9%B1%C3_%BE%DF%B0%A3%B0%B3%C0%E5.jpg?type=w3\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>이렇게해서.</p>\r\n<p>오늘 </p>\r\n<p>5월 23일.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>경복궁에 갔다오겠습니다. ^^</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>어두워서.. 사진찍으면 잘 나오려나 모르겠네요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>.</p>\r\n<p>웹상에서는 야간개장이 몇일간만 하고는 끝나나보더군요</p>\r\n<p>5월 27일까지인가?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>저는 어제 아들이 얘기할 때... </p>\r\n<p>그래.. 천천히.. 사람들 다 다녀가고 나면 우리도 가볼까</p>\r\n<p>생각했는데.</p>\r\n<p>그게 아니었네요 ㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
